dian.com%2Fpolitics%2F2008%2Foct%2F29%2Fpolice-daviddavis&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ANational+Black+Police+Association+%28United+Kingdom%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.law.berkeley.edu/centers/bccj/conferences/policereform/index.html/\">http://www.law.berkeley.edu/centers/bccj/conferences/policereform/index.html/</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20070610060734/http://www.law.berkeley.edu/centers/bccj/conferences/policereform/Wilson%20paper.doc\">https://web.archive.org/web/20070610060734/http://www.law.berkeley.edu/centers/bccj/conferences/policereform/Wilson%20paper.doc</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/comment/columnists/guest_contributors/article7021089.ece,\"><i>A black police association is a bad, outdated idea Why partition members of the same profession along the lines of skin colour?</i>, The Times</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/comment/columnists/minette_marrin/article4926558.ece\"><i>A black police association \u2013 now that is racism in action</i>, The Times</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.nbpa.co.uk/about-us/history/\">\"History\"</a>. National Black Police Association (Official website)<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">28 March</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=History&amp;rft.pub=National+Black+Police+Association+%28Official+website%29&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbpa.co.uk%2Fabout-us%2Fhistory%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ANational+Black+Police+Association+%28United+Kingdom%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Scheerhout, John (21 January 2010). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/news/greater-manchester-news/cop-vows-to-challenge-prejudice-881124\">\"Cop vows to challenge prejudice\"</a>. Manchester Evening News (MEN)<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">28 March</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Cop+vows+to+challenge+prejudice&amp;rft.date=2010-01-21&amp;rft.aulast=Scheerhout&amp;rft.aufirst=John&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.manchestereveningnews.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fgreater-manchester-news%2Fcop-vows-to-challenge-prejudice-881124&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ANational+Black+Police+Association+%28United+Kingdom%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/inde